      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start for my report. Specifically regarding the \"vibrant street life\" and \"community connections\" part—are there studies that show high-density zoning is the most effective way to build social cohesion, or is it more of a general theory? I want to make sure my argument is solid.",
